Tip
: even if you download a ready-made binary for your platform, it makes sense to also download the
source
. This lets you browse the standard library (the subdirectory
Lib
) and the standard collections of demos (
Demo
) and tools (
Tools
) that come with it. There's a lot you can learn from the source!
